The spider crawled up on Drillbits shoulder and curled up into a ball 
to blend in with Drillbits armor. he scanned the battlefield for the 
enemy even though the enemy wasn't very aparent since they were all 
Predacons. he bit Drillbit again to relay another message. 

"Keep up your persuit, you have them on the run and at a 
disadvantage." he looked around some more "Just watch where your 
troops are and don't let them get spread to thin."
